24/04/2005
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- Bulgaria's Central Electoral Commission announced Friday (22 April) that the campaign for the 25 June parliamentary elections would formally open on 25 May.
All political parties and coalitions which want to participate must register by 9 May and submit the newly introduced deposit -- 10,000 euros for parties and 20,000 euros for coalitions.
(Mediapool, BNT - 22/04/05)
